{"tid":1328743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真Post) 有幾多人 追星得黎又好清醒","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T23:28:58.000Z","uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f1e94a79d1210cdb859cc62c941e4fb3906110","tid":1328743,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:13:47.000Z","msg":"我個人黎講 :<br />\nGugudan香港場見過真人之後<br />\n體驗過個後遺症 (個份傷心欲絕)之後<br />\n<br />\n我問左自己幾個問題:<br />\n<br />\n1) 係咪真係咁大件事?<br />\n2) 傷心❤個理由係咩? (見佢真人理應 開心到仆街)<br />\n<br />\n最後諗通左<br />\n不如就直接作曲過去支持<br />\n最後成為左我學作曲的最基本動力<br />\n之後愛上左作曲<br />\n音樂變左我基本動<br />\n<br />\n所以我依家好清醒 <br />\n對明星依家野冇咩大感受了<br />\n因為人生有大把更重要的事要做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我愛❤雨琦</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我愛❤美延</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9BR1eks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9BR1eks.jpg&h=7f6c3dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1Hr9T6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1Hr9T6.jpg&h=a3b30539&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e1595ae290601014ad2a77c5f0da7542debbc12","tid":1328743,"uid":555,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智仔死無全屍落地獄"},{"pid":"5bc811e8ef8b9ef2645c8b6249ac9e98076b3474","tid":1328743,"uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"8e1595ae290601014ad2a77c5f0da7542debbc12","tid":1328743,"uid":555,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智仔死